name: whenUserWithoutCredentialsClicksOnNHSLoginButtonAndEntersPasswordAndSecondFactorOnNHSLoginPageThenTheyGetRedirectedToTheDashboard
description: When user clicks on Log in with NHS Login button and browser is redirected to mocked NHS authorization server then 1) mock calls back OpenID client URL with auth token, 2) mock exchanges auth token to access token, 3) mock returns user info, 4) mock uploads new client_user_metadata, 5) user arrives to NHS Login page, 6) user enters his PKB password associated with his email address and second factor, 7) user arrives to the dashboard.
